metadata.name: logo
metadata.description:
This is a project to create a new city in Metaverse by forming a community under "Ambitious One City", a new city created by ambitious creators, centered on creators from Japan and overseas.
All the works created by the artists participating in the community have been converted to NFT.
A world full of creativity, with the entire city made of "NFT".
It is an art tourist spot that visitors can purchase or sell on their own.
